{"tid":2085024,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"[手足的故事] 認罪囚 4 年 青年入獄前伴病母走人生最後一程","createTime":"2020-06-29T15:30:25.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-29T16:50:50.000Z","uid":128923,"like":25,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"238c84719828b1a741f3417a2875d6b1d39e8348","tid":2085024,"uid":128923,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-29T15:30:25.000Z","msg":"多謝立場肯為咁多位手足做專訪，無論係姚手足，清潔工手足，岩岩放監既手足，等我地知道，每一個都係有血有肉既人，有自已既故事，而唔係法官眼中既暴徒 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n//他從沒想過，被還柙七個月後，母親的病會惡化至此，「由媽咪可以同我傾到計，可以同我講吓笑，之後我出返嚟，就已經係見到佢瞓喺病床，同我傾唔到計，嗰吓接受唔到，好自責&hellip;&hellip;接受唔到媽咪惡化到呢個地步，同我上一次見佢落差太大。」<br />\n<br />\n姚少康保釋外出的第七日，母親病逝。他說，唯一安慰是至少可以陪媽媽走最後一段路，辦理好的喪禮。<br />\n<br />\n與母親相處的最後七天，他特別珍而重之。每日起床後，他都會跟媽媽說「早晨」，下午他會學習餵食物給媽媽吃，跟她說說笑話；晚上他會與媽媽吃晚餐，睡覺前會說「晚安」及親她額頭，他說媽媽會笑。<br />\n<br />\n這七天留下的，除了回憶，還有一張齊齊整整的全家幅。//<br />\n<br />\n//他知道將有一段時間無法照顧父親，只可趁著這額外得來的時間，盡力為父親打點一切。在保釋期的「最後的日子」，他邀請朋友到家中聚聚，讓爸爸認識自己的朋友，亦託付他們空閒時探望爸爸，與他吃飯聊天，「等佢唔好咁多時間自己一個，好驚佢自己一個就會亂諗，會諗埋一邊。」//<br />\n<br />\n//他告訴記者，入獄前的最後一夜他跟朋友和爸爸吃飯，買了蛋糕，慶祝他下個月生日。上庭前說起爸爸，他的眼眶紅了起來，「唔捨得，叫佢唔好擔心，唔敢講太多，驚影響到個情緒。」開庭前，記者一直找不到姚父的身影，他沒有站在姚少康附近，兩父子似乎在保持距離，深怕觸碰到對方的淚腺。<br />\n<br />\n直至臨進入法院一刻，姚少康終於走向父親，在法院外的樓梯上，緊緊抱著爸爸。哭了出來。//<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/專訪-圖擲汽油彈縱火認罪囚-4-年-青年入獄前伴病母走人生最後一程/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%E5%B0%88%E8%A8%AA-%E5%9C%96%E6%93%B2%E6%B1%BD%E6%B2%B9%E5%BD%88%E7%B8%B1%E7%81%AB%E8%AA%8D%E7%BD%AA%E5%9B%9A-4-%E5%B9%B4-%E9%9D%92%E5%B9%B4%E5%85%A5%E7%8D%84%E5%89%8D%E4%BC%B4%E7%97%85%E6%AF%8D%E8%B5%B0%E4%BA%BA%E7%94%9F%E6%9C%80%E5%BE%8C%E4%B8%80%E7%A8%8B%2F&d=BZN1wbl1lFElyj%2BXlEN3CJzZIytzq3Xhz5Kp58Ixet8%3D&h=e81d9499\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%E5%B0%88%E8%A8%AA-%E5%9C%96%E6%93%B2%E6%B1%BD%E6%B2%B9%E5%BD%88%E7%B8%B1%E7%81%AB%E8%AA%8D%E7%BD%AA%E5%9B%9A-4-%E5%B9%B4-%E9%9D%92%E5%B9%B4%E5%85%A5%E7%8D%84%E5%89%8D%E4%BC%B4%E7%97%85%E6%AF%8D%E8%B5%B0%E4%BA%BA%E7%94%9F%E6%9C%80%E5%BE%8C%E4%B8%80%E7%A8%8B%2F&h=ddc90297\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/專訪-圖擲汽油彈縱火認罪囚-4-年-青年入獄前伴病母走人生最後一程/</a>"},{"pid":"2c4d33854a7007f67377209042b6ae45703692c0","tid":2085024,"uid":128923,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-29T15:31:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.thestandnews.com/media/photos/cache/2_GF_dHzui_1200x0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thestandnews.com%2Fmedia%2Fphotos%2Fcache%2F2_GF_dHzui_1200x0.png&h=d97500e8&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"140c4ae3c535818e69cec803126776075cad3eb6","tid":2085024,"uid":54517,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-29T15:39:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"abd03f388d2e98626ce1c5639ac5e27148c92081","tid":2085024,"uid":128923,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"140c4ae3c535818e69cec803126776075cad3eb6","tid":2085024,"uid":54517,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-29T15:39:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-29T15:39:53.000Z","msg":"睇到想喊<br />\n要去到得番7日命先可以保釋 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"23c07c7cf1e3e3a1f7c1f991c2f3f4b84ea9f405","tid":2085024,"uid":13514,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-29T15:40:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6a37bfe1114e09f2fc0e38222fa0f165adca2b50","tid":2085024,"uid":249703,"like":0,"di